  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Under the joint efforts of genetic and intensive expert, to establish the high-throughput
      whole exon sequencing(WES) and analysis all the possible pathogenic genes. To provide patient
      with the appropriate treatment for genetic disease. Besides, it can identify the genetic
      factor of idiosyncrasy or susceptibility to explain the medical difficulties and give
      patients personalized advice.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
